      <abstract>
        <p>This paper describes the synthesis of 3-methyl-1-morpholin-4-ylmethyl-2,6-diphenylpiperidin-4-one from 3-methyl-2,6-diphenylpiperidin-4-one. The synthesized compound was characterized by FT-IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, EI-MS and elemental analysis.</p>
      </abstract>
